{"tid":1676262,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩畢業搵緊工既手足，其實應唔應該大方承認有上街？","createTime":"2019-10-26T10:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:41:00.000Z","uid":6063,"like":70,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2de8834c5c573514c2451f20bc9a956549b5a7d1","tid":1676262,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"我好想請手足，幫幫同路人搵工<br />\n但公司規矩in人要班仆街hr 坐埋係隔離（極藍），姐係最少兩人坐board，我做部門經理都冇得話哂事<br />\n<br />\n咁早兩日in左個岩岩畢業既女手足<br />\n我本身都feel 到係手足想請，但點知佢比hr問多兩問就大方承認佢有上街同埋做文宣<br />\n唉果下都深知不妙<br />\n<br />\n果然一in完hr 就話唔請得<br />\n我好自責比唔到份工佢<br />\n<br />\n我想講既係，其實係同路人真係一個眼神一個感應就知道... <br />\n<br />\n&quot;手足見工用港豬mode 大家交場戲就得&quot;<br />\n有錯隨便屌，我改"},{"pid":"88f12fe379582a3f271eeec67ad9f46bd6df5d2b","tid":1676262,"uid":296068,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"啱呀，黃絲通常都偏後生，年輕人普遍直腸直肚城府唔深。<br />\n有陣時要以退為進，先避鋒芒。"},{"pid":"f8befc3a25053f457c9927a468b4b2adabb75ce2","tid":1676262,"uid":92653,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"屌鳩班hr得唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55e7f8fc23bf83cf930d8e6f5a94f5897241af3","tid":1676262,"uid":263038,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"又會咁on9嘅<br />\n唔好話見工啦<br />\n返工都要扮港豬啦<br />\n我喺同事面前扮哂政治冷感<br />\n就算係黃嘅同事問我有冇發夢我都係答話唔夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0b36a1dbf97a713a52311252f6a4dd59eb050d","tid":1676262,"uid":92653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9212b2378b0f9a377158133bd59f03fc1cc0e45a","tid":1676262,"uid":58351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況真係要能屈能伸， 唔搵錢邊度有錢捐錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/